OL,7,FMr Millington was made boss of the
OL,8,Fsouth Wales service in February, on
OL,9,Fsecondment from the north. However,
OL,10,Fwithin days of his appointment, he was
OL,11,Fthe subject of bullying allegations.
OL,12,FHe denies the allegations.
OL,14,FReplying to Mr ap Iorwerth's question,
OL,15,FMr Gething said he had not seen the
OL,16,Freport.
