OL,7,FIn Tuesday's questions to the First
OL,8,FMinister, Rhun ap Iorwerth said "when
OL,9,FStuart Millington was appointed the
OL,10,FNorth Wales Chief Fire Office Dawn
OL,11,FDocx issued a statement and I quote:
OL,12,F'While it would be improper for us to
OL,13,Fcomment on any particular grievance'.
OL,15,F"We were told that the complaints Mr
OL,16,FMillington was facing represented only
OL,17,F'learning opportunities or minor
OL,18,Flearning opportunities'."
